Ext.data.JsonP['Performance_Issues']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Performance Issues</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-33622331\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Performance Issues</h1>\n    <p>If you are having issues with the speed of Studio, this document provides information you can use to diagnose the problem.    </p>\n    <p>    </p>\n<ul class=\"toc-indentation \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Performance_Issues-section-src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-BuildingWorkspacetakinglongerthanexpected\">Building Workspace taking longer than expected</a>    </p>\n<ul class=\"toc-indentation \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Performance_Issues-section-src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Studioisindexingextrafiles\">Studio is indexing extra files</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Performance_Issues-section-src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Studioisencounteringanexceptionduringindexing\">Studio is encountering an exception during indexing</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Performance_Issues-section-src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Avalidatororbuilderisenabledthatistakingalongtimetoprocesseachfile\">A validator or builder is enabled that is taking a long time to process each file</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Performance_Issues-section-src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Theindexiscorrupt\">The index is corrupt</a>    </p>\n<ul class=\"toc-indentation \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Performance_Issues-section-src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Localprojectindex\">Local project index</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Performance_Issues-section-src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Globalindex\">Global index</a>    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Performance_Issues-section-src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Ifthatstilldoesnothelp...\">If that still does not help...</a>    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Performance_Issues-section-src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-HighCPUusage\">High CPU usage</a>    </p>\n<ul class=\"toc-indentation \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Performance_Issues-section-src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-VisualVMinstallation\">VisualVM installation</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Performance_Issues-section-src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-FindtheStudioprocess\">Find the Studio process</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Performance_Issues-section-src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-StartrecordingCPUusage\">Start recording CPU usage</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Performance_Issues-section-src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Alternateapproaches\">Alternate approaches</a>    </p>\n</li></ul></li></ul>    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-BuildingWorkspacetakinglongerthanexpected\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Building Workspace taking longer than expected</span></h2>\n    <p>There are several reasons why building a workspace could take a long time to index. We suggest trying the steps below in succession to resolve the issue.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Studioisindexingextrafiles\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Studio is indexing extra files</span></h3>\n    <p>It&apos;s possible that you have a large directory of generated or resource files that don&apos;t need to be indexed. To exclude items from indexing:    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Right-click on a project&apos;s folder.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Select Build &gt; Exclude from build.    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Studioisencounteringanexceptionduringindexing\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Studio is encountering an exception during indexing</span></h3>\n    <p>Check the Studio log file. It may be a bug, or the index is corrupt.    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Help &gt; Studio &gt; View Log File    </p>\n</li></ol>    <p>If you notice things like , it&apos;s likely your index is corrupt. See below.    </p>\n    <p>If you notice issues mentioned in <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/APSTUD-2260\" target=\"_blank\">APSTUD-2260</a> (    <span style=\"color: #2b4771;\">\nUTFDataFormatException in DiskIndex.readString()    </span>\n), it is likely your index is corrupt. See <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Performance_Issues-section-src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Theindexiscorrupt\">The index is corrupt</a> section below.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Avalidatororbuilderisenabledthatistakingalongtimetoprocesseachfile\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>A validator or builder is enabled that is taking a long time to process each file</span></h3>\n    <p>Validators for JavaScript (like JSLint) can take a <i class=\" \">long</i> time to process many files. You may wish to only have them enabled on reconcile only    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Open Preference &gt; Studio &gt; Validation    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Disable items on &quot;build&quot; that seem like likely culprits    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Select OK    </p>\n</li></ol>    <p>Studio will rebuild using the new settings.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Theindexiscorrupt\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>The index is corrupt</span></h3>\n    <p>Studio indexes your files in order to collect metadata about the project for use in content assist. There are two indexes.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-4 \" id=\"src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Localprojectindex\">\n        <h4 class=\"heading \"><span>Local project index</span></h4>\n    <p>This stores the contents for your local project    </p>\n    <p>To clear your local project index    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><strong class=\" \">Project &gt; Clean...</strong>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Either choose your project, or &quot;All Projects&quot;    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-4 \" id=\"src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Globalindex\">\n        <h4 class=\"heading \"><span>Global index</span></h4>\n    <p>This contains information about the core JavaScript libraries, etc.    </p>\n    <p>To clear your global index    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Find your workspace directory on disk    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Locate the .metadata folder indside (you may need to show hidden files)    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Delete .metadata/.plugins/com.aptana.index.core/*.index (index file/files for the JS, HTML etc.).    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Delete .metadata/.plugins/com.aptana.editor.php/*.index (index file/files for PHP).    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Restart Studio    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Ifthatstilldoesnothelp...\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>If that still does not help...</span></h3>\n    <p>There are diagnoses you can perform that will help us understand the issue:    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Turn on Show Normally Hidden Processes: <strong class=\" \">Preferences </strong>&gt;<strong class=\" \"> Studio </strong>&gt;<strong class=\" \"> Troubleshooting </strong>&gt;<strong class=\" \"> Show Normally Hidden Processes</strong>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>In the same preference page, turn on the following:    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Debug Level: All    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Debug specific components    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>com.aptana.core/debug/builder    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>com.aptana.core/debug/builder/indexer    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>com.aptana.core/debug/builder/participants    </p>\n</li></ol></li></ol></li><li class=\" \">    <p>Then, clear the log file: <strong class=\" \">Help</strong> &gt; <strong class=\" \">Studio</strong> &gt; <strong class=\" \">Clear Log File</strong>.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Restart Studio    </p>\n</li></ol>    <p>Attach your findings to <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/APSTUD-2050\" target=\"_blank\">APSTUD-2050</a> (    <span style=\"color: #2b4771;\">\n&quot;Building Workspace&quot; job takes a while to complete    </span>\n). You should see entries like:    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox programlisting defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\">\n                <div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\">\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">!ENTRY com.aptana.core </code><code class=\"value\">1</code><code class=\"plain\"> </code><code class=\"value\">0</code><code class=\"plain\"> </code><code class=\"value\">2012</code><code class=\"plain\">-</code><code class=\"value\">08</code><code class=\"plain\">-</code><code class=\"value\">15</code><code class=\"plain\"> </code><code class=\"value\">14</code><code class=\"plain\">:</code><code class=\"value\">44</code><code class=\"plain\">:</code><code class=\"value\">09.007</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">!MESSAGE (Build </code><code class=\"value\">0.0</code><code class=\"plain\">.</code><code class=\"value\">0</code><code class=\"plain\">.qualifier) [INFO] com.aptana.core/debug/builder Performing incremental unified build on project </code><code class=\"string\">&apos;geolocationClient&apos;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\">&#xA0;</div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">!ENTRY com.aptana.buildpath.core </code><code class=\"value\">1</code><code class=\"plain\"> </code><code class=\"value\">0</code><code class=\"plain\"> </code><code class=\"value\">2012</code><code class=\"plain\">-</code><code class=\"value\">08</code><code class=\"plain\">-</code><code class=\"value\">15</code><code class=\"plain\"> </code><code class=\"value\">14</code><code class=\"plain\">:</code><code class=\"value\">44</code><code class=\"plain\">:</code><code class=\"value\">09.069</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">!MESSAGE (Build </code><code class=\"value\">0.0</code><code class=\"plain\">.</code><code class=\"value\">0</code><code class=\"plain\">.qualifier) [INFO] com.aptana.core/debug/builder/participants Executed build participant </code><code class=\"string\">&apos;Index Build Participant&apos;</code><code class=\"plain\"> on </code><code class=\"string\">&apos;file:/Users/ingo/Documents/Aptana%20Workspaces/Aptana%20Studio%203%20Workspace/geolocationClient/LICENSE&apos;</code><code class=\"plain\"> in </code><code class=\"value\">10.842</code><code class=\"plain\"> ms.</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\">&#xA0;</div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">...</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\">&#xA0;</div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">!ENTRY com.aptana.core </code><code class=\"value\">1</code><code class=\"plain\"> </code><code class=\"value\">0</code><code class=\"plain\"> </code><code class=\"value\">2012</code><code class=\"plain\">-</code><code class=\"value\">08</code><code class=\"plain\">-</code><code class=\"value\">15</code><code class=\"plain\"> </code><code class=\"value\">14</code><code class=\"plain\">:</code><code class=\"value\">44</code><code class=\"plain\">:</code><code class=\"value\">09.556</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">!MESSAGE (Build </code><code class=\"value\">0.0</code><code class=\"plain\">.</code><code class=\"value\">0</code><code class=\"plain\">.qualifier) [INFO] com.aptana.core/debug/builder Finished unified build of </code><code class=\"string\">&apos;geolocationClient&apos;</code><code class=\"plain\">. Took </code><code class=\"value\">589.057</code><code class=\"plain\"> ms.</code></div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-HighCPUusage\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>High CPU usage</span></h2>\n    <p>Diagnosing high CPU usage is relatively straightforward, but requires a small amount of setup. However, the information gained here is invaluable to the developers.    </p>\n    <p>In order to do so, we will use a tool called VisualVM. It is included with many Java distributions, so you may not even need to install it.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-VisualVMinstallation\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>VisualVM installation</span></h3>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Check to see if it&apos;s already installed. You may be able to run &quot;visualvm&quot; or &quot;jvisualvm&quot; on the command line.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>If not, follow the steps <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"http://visualvm.java.net/download.html\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>which involve downloading a .zip file and running the program inside.    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Ubuntu users can use <tt class=\" \">apt-get virtualvm</tt>    </p>\n</li></ol></li><li class=\" \">    <p>It will go through a brief step calibrating your machine.    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-FindtheStudioprocess\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Find the Studio process</span></h3>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Shut down other Java applications other than Studio to make it easiest to find Studio in the list.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Once Visual VM has started, you will see at least two processes in the left-hand column. Studio is likely to be the &quot;Unknown Application&quot;.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Double-click on that item.    </p>\n</li></ol>    <p>A pane opens showing details about the process    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-StartrecordingCPUusage\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Start recording CPU usage</span></h3>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Switch to the &quot;Sampler&quot; tab, and click &quot;CPU&quot;.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Sort by &quot;Self Time (CPU)&quot; to see if what are the most active threads.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Start replicating the item which provokes CPU usage.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Once you are complete, click the &quot;snapshot&quot; button.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click on the small disk icon to the left to save the file to disk. Give it a descriptive name.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Attach that file to a JIRA ticket.    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-33622331_PerformanceIssues-Alternateapproaches\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Alternate approaches</span></h3>\n    <p>Two other things to try that might highlight the issue    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Turn on <strong class=\" \">Preferences &gt; Studio &gt; Troubleshooting &gt; Show Normally Hidden Processes</strong>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>In the same preference page, turn on    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Debug Level: All    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Debug specific components    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>com.aptana.core/debug/shell    </p>\n</li></ol></li></ol></li><li class=\" \">    <p>Help &gt; Studio &gt; Clear Log File    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Cause the CPU usage spike.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Check both the Progress View and the log file to see if any obvious processes are causing the problems.    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=33622331\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Performance Issues"});